# graphify ignore patterns for the persistent Vault (gitignore syntax).
#
# Minified SilverBullet plug bundles are single-line transpiled blobs that
# graphify's AST extractor mis-parses into a god-node: silverbullet-pdf.plug.js
# (2.5 MB) alone produced ~900 edges and dominated god_nodes in the unified
# global graph. The vault-extract subagent ingests Library/Codeflare/*.plug.js
# into ~/.graphify/global-graph.json, so without this file the plug bundles
# drown the real vault notes. These are vendored build artifacts, not content.
*.plug.js
